dc_title_s: Streams, Rivers, and Canals, Placer County, California, 2020
dc_description_s: This line shapefile contains streams, rivers and canals of Placer County California. This data set was digized from 1:24000 USGS quadrangles ranging in date. The dataset contains attributes that inculde stream type, perennial or intermittant, Strahler stream order and watershed.. This layer is part of a collection of public geospatial datasets produced by the Placer County GIS Division.
